            <h3>My Assistant</h3>
            <p><strong>Overview:</strong></p>
            <p><strong>My Assistant</strong> is a versatile Python-based tool designed to streamline various tasks and provide useful functionalities. It integrates with different applications, performs web searches, manages files, and even entertains with games and jokes. This project aims to enhance productivity and provide a seamless user experience.</p>
            <p><strong>Features:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Search on Wikipedia:</strong> Look up information on Wikipedia.</li>
                <li><strong>Open Apps:</strong> Launch applications such as YouTube, Chrome, PowerPoint, File Explorer, Recycle Bin, Stack Overflow, and Email.</li>
